{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"AnimationEvent","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Construtor</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Propriedades</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/animationName\"><code>animationName</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime\"><code>elapsedTime</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/pseudoElement\"><code>pseudoElement</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Herança:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>Esta é uma <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Guidelines/Conventions_definitions#experimental\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">tecnologia experimental (en-US)</a></strong><br>Verifique a <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">tabela de compatibilidade entre Navegadores</a> cuidadosamente antes de usar essa funcionalidade em produção.</p></div><p></p>\n\n<p>A interface&nbsp;<strong><code>AnimationEvent</code></strong>&nbsp; representa eventos provendo&nbsp;informações&nbsp;relacionadas a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/Guide/CSS/Using_CSS_animations/\" class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\">animações</a>.</p>\n\n<p><code><svg viewBox=\"-1 -1 650 42\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMinYMin meet\">\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\">\n    <rect x=\"0\" y=\"0\" width=\"75\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#fff\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"37.5\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      Event\n    </text>\n  </a>\n  <line x1=\"75\" y1=\"14\" x2=\"105\" y2=\"14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" \"=\"\"></line>\n  <polyline points=\"75,14 85,9 85,19 75,14\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" fill=\"#fff\"></polyline>\n  <a style=\"text-decoration: none;\" xlink:href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent\" aria-current=\"page\">\n    <rect x=\"105\" y=\"0\" width=\"112\" height=\"25\" fill=\"#F4F7F8\" stroke=\"#D4DDE4\" stroke-width=\"2px\"></rect>\n    <text x=\"161\" y=\"16\" font-size=\"10px\" fill=\"#4D4E53\" text-anchor=\"middle\">\n      AnimationEvent\n    </text>\n  </a></svg></code></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propriedades","title":"Propriedades","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Também propriedades herdadas&nbsp;pelo&nbsp;pai&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></code></em>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"animationevent.animationname_somente_leitura\"><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/animationName\"><code>AnimationEvent.animationName</code></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></code></dt>\n <dd>O <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a> contém&nbsp;o&nbsp;valor do&nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/animation-name\"><code>animation-name</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a>&nbsp;propriedade&nbsp;CSS associada com a transição.</dd>\n <dt id=\"animationevent.elapsedtime_somente_leitura\"><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/elapsedTime\"><code>AnimationEvent.elapsedTime</code></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></code></dt>\n <dd><code><font face=\"Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif\">É um ponto flutuante</font></code>&nbsp;dado&nbsp;pela quantidade de tempo que a animação está rodando, em segundos, quando&nbsp;esse evento termina, excluindo o tempo em que animação esteve pausada. Para&nbsp;o evento&nbsp;<code>\"animationstart\"</code>, <code>elapsedTime</code>&nbsp;é&nbsp;<code>0.0</code>&nbsp;a não ser que haja um valor negativo para&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/CSS/animation-delay\"><code>animation-delay</code></a></code>, nesse caso o evento terminará com&nbsp;<code>elapsedTime</code> contendo&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>(-1 * </code><em>delay</em><code>)</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"animationevent.pseudoelement_somente_leitura\"><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/pseudoElement\"><code>AnimationEvent.pseudoElement</code></a> <span title=\"Este valor não pode ser alterado.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Somente leitura </span></code></dt>\n <dd>Um<code> <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a>&nbsp;</code>começa com&nbsp;&nbsp;<code>'::'</code>, contendo o nome do&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/Pseudo-elements\">pseudo-elemento</a>&nbsp;onde a animação roda. Se a animação não rodar no pseudo-elemento mas no elemento, então teremos um <em>string </em>vazio <code>' '</code>.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"constructores","title":"Constructores","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"animationevent\"><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent\" title=\"AnimationEvent()\"><code>AnimationEvent()</code></a></code></dt>\n <dd>Cria um evento&nbsp;<code>AnimationEvent</code>&nbsp;com os dados parâmetros.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"métodos","title":"Métodos","isH3":false,"content":"<p><em>Também herda métodos do pai&nbsp;<code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></code></em>.</p>\n\n<dl>\n <dt id=\"animationevent.initanimationevent\"><code><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/conflicting/Web/API/AnimationEvent/AnimationEvent\"><code>AnimationEvent.initAnimationEvent()</code></a> <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></code></dt>\n <dd>Inicializa um&nbsp;<code>AnimationEvent criado usando diminuído&nbsp;</code><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Document/createEvent\"><code>Document.createEvent(\"AnimationEvent\")</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a> método.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificação</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Estado</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://drafts.csswg.org/css-animations-1/#AnimationEvent-interface\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS Animations Level 1<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'AnimationEvent' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-wd\">Rascunho atual</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td>\n    <p>1.0 <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></p>\n\n    <p>43.0</p>\n   </td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/6\" title=\"Released on 2011-08-16.\">6.0</a> (6.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td>12 <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">o (en-US)</a></span><br>\n    12.10<br>\n    15.0 <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n   <td>4.0 <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>AnimationEvent() constructor</td>\n   <td>\n    <p>43.0</p>\n   </td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/23\" title=\"Released on 2013-08-06.\">23.0</a> (23.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>initAnimationEvent() <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td>1.0</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/6\" title=\"Released on 2011-08-16.\">6.0</a> (6.0)<br>\n    Removed in <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/23\" title=\"Released on 2013-08-06.\">23.0</a> (23.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td>12</td>\n   <td>4.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>pseudoelement</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/23\" title=\"Released on 2013-08-06.\">23.0</a> (23.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Basic support</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n   <td>6.0 (6.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td>12 <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">o (en-US)</a></span><br>\n    12.10<br>\n    15.0 <span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span><span class=\"inlineIndicator prefixBox prefixBoxInline\" title=\"prefix\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/Vendor_Prefix\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">webkit (en-US)</a></span></td>\n   <td>43.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>AnimationEvent() constructor</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>23.0 (23.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>43.0</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>initAnimationEvent() <svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td>6.0 (6.0)<br>\n    Removed in 23.0 (23.0)</td>\n   <td>10.0</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>pseudoelement</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>23.0 (23.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sect1","title":"&nbsp;","isH3":false,"content":"","titleAsText":" "}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Animations/Using_CSS_animations\">Usando animações CSS</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Propriedades","id":"propriedades"},{"text":"Constructores","id":"constructores"},{"text":"Métodos","id":"métodos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"&nbsp;","id":"sect1"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"A interface AnimationEvent  representa eventos provendo informações relacionadas a animações.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"AnimationEvent","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"AnimationEvent","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"AnimationEvent","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"AnimationEvent","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"AnimationEvent","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"AnimationEvent","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"AnimationEvent","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"AnimationEvent","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/api/animationevent","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/api/animationevent/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API","title":"APIs da Web"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/AnimationEvent","title":"AnimationEvent"}],"pageTitle":"AnimationEvent - APIs da Web | MDN","noIndexing":false}}